Standards-Version: 3.9.2
Homepage: http://www.finnie.org/software/oui/

Package: oui
Architecture: all
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, perl
Description: Searches A locally-installed IEEE OUI database
 oui searches a system IEEE OUI database.  With any options, it takes a
 OUI or MAC address in a variety of formats (uppercase, lowercase, 
 colon delimited, dash delimited, no delimiter).  If an OUI entry is 
 found, the OUI and organization is printed.

